{
  "chapter": 13,
  "chapter_summary": "沈三娘带伤回屋，被马芳铃察觉并追问她夜半外出的对象，马芳铃因傅红雪而失态。马空群忽然来唤沈三娘上楼，在书房中让她见到被带回的翠浓。沈三娘坦承昨夜去找傅红雪查证凶手，并揭露公孙断伤她。马空群却早已看穿她姓花，是花白凤之妹，也知道翠浓为她传递消息。他逼问白天羽遗孤究竟是叶开还是傅红雪，并因万马堂连番死人决定揭穿秘密。沈三娘反问杀人者死时刺中他的恐惧。最终马空群没有杀她，只让她离开，沈三娘在痛苦与复杂情感中明白自己也许不该来。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你……你受了伤？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你知道我刚才出去过？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你放心，我也是个女人，我可以装作不知道。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你这里有没有酒，我想喝一杯！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你是什么时候学会喝酒的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你在我这样的年纪，难道还没有学会喝酒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "酒就在那边柜子最下面的一层抽屉里。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我就知道你这里一定有酒藏着，我若是你，晚上睡不着的时候，也会一个人起来喝两杯的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "这两天来，你的确好像已长大了很多。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我本来就已是个大人，所以你一定要告诉我，刚才你出去找的是谁？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你放心，不是叶开。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "是谁？傅红雪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你盯着我干什么？是不是因为我猜对了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你醉了，为什么不回去睡一觉，等清醒了再来找我。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "speaker_name": "马芳铃",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我只不过想知道你是用什么法子勾引他的，那法子一定不错，否则他怎么会看上你这么老的女人。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_fang_ling",
      "text": "你喜欢的难道是他？\n不是叶开？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "三娘，你醒了吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "刚起来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "嗯。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "睡得好不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "不好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "跟我上去好不好？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你知不知道我找你上来做什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "随便你要做什么都没关系。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我若要杀了你呢？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我当然不会杀你，屋里还有个人在等你。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "有人在等我？谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你永远猜不到他是谁的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你们当然是认得的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "现在我已将她带回来了，也免得你以后再三更半夜地去找她。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "我昨天晚上的确出去过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "我要找的人也不是翠浓。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我知道。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "我去找的人是傅红雪！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "我去找他，只因为我总觉得他就是杀死那些人的凶手。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "他不是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "他的确不是，但我在没有查明白之前，总是不能安心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我明白。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "我可以从他对我的态度上看出来，女人天生就有种微妙的感觉，他若恨你，对我的态度也一定不同。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我懂。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "可是他却对我很客气，我去的时候，他虽然显得有些吃惊，我要走的时候，他却并没有留难我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "他是个君子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "只可惜你有个朋友并不是君子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你知道这是被谁打的？",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我不想知道。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你不知道也好，我只不过要你明白，为了你，我什么事都肯做。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "这些年来，你的确为我做了很多事，吃了很多苦。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "这地方本是一片荒漠，没有你，我也许根本就不能将这地方改变得如此美丽，没有人知道你对我的帮助有多么大。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "只要你知道，我就已心满意足了。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我当然知道，你帮助我将这块地方改变得如此美丽，只不过是要我在失去它时觉得更痛苦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你……你……你在说什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我在说一件秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "什么秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你的秘密。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "我……我有什么秘密？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "从你第一天到这里来的时候，我已知道你是谁了！",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你不姓沈，姓花。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "白天羽的外室花白凤，秒是你嫡亲的姐姐。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你……你怎么知道？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你也许不信，但你还未到这里来时，我已见过你，见过你们姐妹和白天羽在一起，那时你还小，你姐姐肚子里却已有了白天羽的孩子。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "白天羽死了后，我也曾找过你们姐妹，但你姐姐却一直隐藏得很好，又有谁能想到你居然到这里来了！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我早已知道你是谁，但却一直没有说出来，你知不知道是为了什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "因为我喜欢你，而且很需要你这样一个女人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "而且还是自己心甘情愿地免费送上门来的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我已早就知道你跟翠浓的关系。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我这边的消息，由翠浓转出去，外边的消息，也是由翠浓转给你的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "你用她这种人来转达消息，倒的确是个聪明的主意。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "只可惜还是早已被你知道。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我一直没有阻止你们，只因为我根本就没有重要的消息给你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你也许还想从我这里得到外面的消息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "只可惜你姐姐比你精明得多，这么多年来，我竟始终查不出她的踪迹。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "所以她直到现在还活着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "她的儿子呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "也还活着。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "现在是不是已经到这里来了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你猜呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 354
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "是叶开，还是傅红雪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 356,
      "line_end": 356
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你猜不出？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "就算你不说，我也有法子知道的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "那么你又何必问我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 362,
      "line_end": 362
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "其实直到今天为止，我还是不想揭穿你的秘密，因为我还是不忍中断我们现在的这种关系。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 364,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "只可惜你现在已到了非揭穿我不可的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 368
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "因为这件事已不能再拖下去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 370,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "既然已拖了十几年，又何妨再拖几天？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我有儿有女，还有几百个兄弟，我不忍眼见着他们再一个个死在我的眼前。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 374,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "昨天晚上又死了多少？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 378
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "死得已够多。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 380,
      "line_end": 380
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你认为谁是凶手？叶开？傅红雪？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "不管凶手是谁，我可以向你保证，他一定逃不了的！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "天网恢恢，疏而不漏，杀人者死……对不对？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 390
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 392
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "那么你自己呢？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好快，又是一天，早膳的时候又到了。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 402,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你今天还吃得下？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "这是我自己订下的规矩，至少我自己不能破坏它！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 408,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "等一等。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你怎么能就这样走了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 416,
      "line_end": 416
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "为什么不能？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你……你准备对我怎么样？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 420,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "不怎么样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 422
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "我不懂你的意思。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 424,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我没有意思。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你既已揭穿了我的隐秘，为什么不杀了我？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 428,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "揭穿你的秘密是一回事，杀你又是另外一回事了I",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 430
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我知道你当然也不能再留在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 434
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你让我走？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 436,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "我为什么不让你走？\n难道我真能杀了你？",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "你既然已准备让我走，为什么又要揭穿我的秘密？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 448
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "那也许只因为我要让你知道，我并不是个呆子。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 450,
      "line_end": 452
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "text": "那也许只因为你已不愿我再留在这里。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 454,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ma_kong_qun",
      "speaker_name": "马空群",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "也许。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 456,
      "line_end": 456
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_cui_nong",
      "speaker_name": "翠浓",
      "listener": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "text": "他既然已让我们走，我们为什么还不走？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shen_san_niang",
      "speaker_name": "沈三娘",
      "listener": "char_cui_nong",
      "text": "当然要走，只不过……也许我根本不该来的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 13,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 486
    }
